============================================================
OPTIMIZER REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Create:

backend/app/backtesting/optimizer.py

Implement:

ParameterOptimizer

Methods:
- expand_grid(parameter_grid: dict) -> list[dict]
- optimize(request: OptimizationRequest) -> OptimizationResult

Rules:
- Cartesian product of parameter values
- Cap total combinations by max_combinations
- Use StrategyLab.run_backtest() for each parameter combination
- Rank by sort_metric
- Supported sort metrics:
  - profit_factor
  - net_profit_percent
  - win_rate
  - expectancy
  - sharpe_like_score
- If unsupported metric, default to profit_factor
- Capture warnings when combinations are truncated

============================================================
STRATEGY PROMOTION REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Create:

backend/app/backtesting/promotion.py

Implement:

StrategyPromotionGate

Method:
- evaluate(result: BacktestResult) -> StrategyPromotionDecision

Promotion gates:
- ALLOW_STRATEGY_PROMOTION must be true
- total_trades >= MIN_PROMOTION_TRADES
- win_rate >= MIN_PROMOTION_WIN_RATE
- profit_factor >= MIN_PROMOTION_PROFIT_FACTOR
- max_drawdown_percent <= MAX_PROMOTION_DRAWDOWN_PERCENT
- consecutive_losses <= MAX_PROMOTION_CONSECUTIVE_LOSSES

Rules:
- If ALLOW_STRATEGY_PROMOTION=false, approved=false
- Return all gate pass/fail states
- Never auto-enable live trading
- Never disable Guardian risk system
- Promotion only marks strategy as validated candidate

